{
  "stem": "20142.6",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They wanted to devastate as many homes, as many houses as they could without-- because they couldn't get response from the Jewish community, from the Jewish people in Warsaw Ghetto, to cooperate of-- for the-- for the deportation.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And none of the units wanted to get into ghetto and plunder or look for things.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they simply were devastating it [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In the meantime, they were-- we were training people and whatever help we were getting from the outside of the Polish people with whom we made-- contact was made to get the weapons for fighting and so on.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was just a drop in the bucket.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Through the sewer lines.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After I came to ghetto through the sewer lines, I never went through the sewer lines again.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "However, I believe that [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Vladka Meed and Ben Meed, who were present in the Warsaw ghetto uprising, were-- got out of the ghetto through the sewer lines.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that was not a simple encounter, as I described.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You had to be totally prepared and know the layout of the sewer lines to know where to get out.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If you were staying for a long period of time, you were absorbed by the gasses and you couldn't survive under no condition.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There were many cases that people were looking for the sewer line hoping to escape, but could not survive without proper orientation and total preparation.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Depressed.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] there was depression, definitely.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the spirit of being able to fight for the life was perhaps greater or greater value than-- to them at that time than just giving up and marching to the Umschlagplatz.",
      "word_count": 36
    }
  ],
